---
import PageShell from "../components/PageShell.astro";
---

<PageShell title="About | The 100 Hackathoner">
  <section class="page-hero container">
    <h1>Learning in public, one hackathon at a time.</h1>
    <p>
      Sayyid Khan is a Singapore-based AI builder documenting the road to 100
      hackathons while moving from builder mindset toward founder/operator
      judgement.
    </p>
  </section>

  <section class="section rail">
    <div class="container split">
      <h2 class="serif">Why this exists</h2>
      <div>
        <p>
          Most portfolios show outcomes. This site keeps the whole record: the
          idea, the people, the chaos, the build, the failure, the win, and the
          lesson.
        </p>
        <p>
          Hackathons compress ambition into a deadline. They reveal whether a
          problem matters, whether the prototype works, whether the story lands,
          and whether the builder is becoming sharper.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section container beliefs">
    <h2 class="serif">Operating Beliefs</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>Building is a form of self-discovery.</li>
      <li>Repetition creates luck.</li>
      <li>Shipping reveals truth.</li>
      <li>Failure compounds into instinct.</li>
      <li>Purpose is discovered through motion.</li>
    </ul>
  </section>
</PageShell>

<style>
  .page-hero {
    padding: 86px 0 92px;
  }

  h1 {
    max-width: 980px;
    margin: 0;
    color: var(--ink);
    font-size: clamp(3.4rem, 8vw, 8rem);
    font-weight: 950;
    letter-spacing: -0.035em;
    line-height: 0.96;
  }

  .page-hero p {
    max-width: 760px;
    margin: 28px 0 0;
    color: var(--muted);
    font-size: 1.16rem;
    line-height: 1.75;
  }

  .split {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: minmax(0, 0.7fr) minmax(300px, 0.85fr);
    gap: 48px;
  }

  h2 {
    margin: 0;
    color: var(--ink);
    font-size: clamp(2.6rem, 5vw, 5.6rem);
    line-height: 0.92;
  }

  p {
    margin: 0 0 18px;
    color: var(--muted);
    font-size: 1.05rem;
    line-height: 1.75;
  }

  .beliefs ul {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(5, minmax(0, 1fr));
    gap: 12px;
    margin: 32px 0 0;
    padding: 0;
    list-style: none;
  }

  li {
    min-height: 150px;
    border-top: 5px solid var(--red);
    background: var(--surface);
    color: var(--muted);
    line-height: 1.55;
    padding: 18px;
  }

  li:nth-child(2) {
    border-color: var(--blue);
  }

  li:nth-child(3) {
    border-color: var(--teal);
  }

  li:nth-child(4) {
    border-color: var(--yellow);
  }

  li:nth-child(5) {
    border-color: var(--black);
  }

  @media (max-width: 900px) {
    .split,
    .beliefs ul {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
  }
</style>
